java based config
1) have an entity-class(HelloWorld here)
2) create a config-class(HelloWorldConfig here) with @Configuration annotation
3) make methods that create beans with @Bean annotations
4) make context from config-class with  ApplicationContext ctx = new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(HelloWorldConfig.class);
5) get beans from context!

Config in multiple classes(@Import):
http://docs.spring.io/spring-javaconfig/docs/1.0.0.M4/reference/html/ch04s03.html

